- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed method in terms of time and memory. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possibility as the paper deals with the representation of large graphs in a low-dimensional space. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly deal with natural language processing, but it does involve the use of LSTM, which is a popular technique in NLP.
